950
00:57:48,528 --> 00:57:51,292
I'm telling ya. I'll get
the C.I.A. And the F.B.I.

951
00:57:51,364 --> 00:57:53,423
You'll be workin' security
at Toys 'R' Us.

952
00:57:53,499 --> 00:57:55,433
- Oh, oh, baby, no, no. No, no!
- Bye-bye, little astronaut.

953
00:57:55,501 --> 00:57:59,437
