955
00:58:05,278 --> 00:58:09,146
- Give me a projected impact.
- East Asia, 11 minutes.

956
00:58:09,215 --> 00:58:12,707
- We're gonna have to warn...
- Warn who? The entire South Pacific?

957
00:58:18,825 --> 00:58:21,760
