958
00:58:27,533 --> 00:58:31,060
[Loud Rumbling]

959
00:58:38,044 --> 00:58:41,070
[People Screaming]

960
00:59:02,235 --> 00:59:04,169
[Phone Rings]

961
00:59:05,838 --> 00:59:07,772
So the whole world knows.

962
00:59:10,009 --> 00:59:12,705
Tell me you've never
let anybody down before.

963
00:59:12,779 --> 00:59:15,009
I never quit yet.

964
00:59:15,081 --> 00:59:18,642
- How's that?
- I guess that'll have to do.

965
00:59:18,718 --> 00:59:21,050
You know somethin'?

966
00:59:21,120 --> 00:59:25,216
I still remember the first,
middle and last name...

967
00:59:25,291 --> 00:59:29,125
of every guy that qualified for the
astronaut program first year I was here.

968
00:59:29,462 --> 00:59:33,091
Thanks.
Twenty-two years later.

969
00:59:33,166 --> 00:59:35,999
Of course,
things were different then.

970
00:59:36,068 --> 00:59:40,937
It wasn't so much about
the paperwork and the politics.

971
00:59:41,007 --> 00:59:42,838
It was all about
getting the job done.

972
00:59:42,909 --> 00:59:47,846
I went into the engineering program.
Kinda had to.

973
00:59:47,914 --> 00:59:50,644
But boy, I wanted to go up there.

974
00:59:50,716 --> 00:59:54,243
I wanted to be one of those guys
with a mission patch on my arm.

975
00:59:55,421 --> 00:59:57,651
I tell you, I'd be on that shuttle
with you, Harry, if I could.

976
00:59:57,723 --> 01:00:00,191
