01:00:07,733 --> 01:00:11,760
- You scared?
- Yeah.

979
01:00:12,738 --> 01:00:15,866
- You?
- Yeah.

980
01:00:15,942 --> 01:00:18,467
Good luck in Florida tomorrow.

981
01:00:18,544 --> 01:00:22,640
[Female Newscaster #1] The death of 50,000
