1058
01:06:05,023 --> 01:06:08,550
The human thirst for excellence,

1059
01:06:08,627 --> 01:06:12,119
- [Translator On Radio]
- Knowledge,

1060
01:06:12,197 --> 01:06:15,963
every step up the ladder of science,

1061
01:06:16,034 --> 01:06:20,903
every adventurous reach into space,

1062
01:06:20,972 --> 01:06:26,569
all of our combined modern technologies and
imaginations, even the wars that we've fought,

1063
01:06:26,645 --> 01:06:29,205
have provided us the tools...

1064
01:06:29,280 --> 01:06:32,613
