1076
01:07:06,584 --> 01:07:10,486
citizens the world over,
see these events through.

1077
01:07:10,555 --> 01:07:15,254
Godspeed and good luck to you.

1078
01:07:22,500 --> 01:07:25,128
Freedom crew. Independence crew.

1079
01:07:30,008 --> 01:07:33,500
- How ya feelin'?
- Uh, good, you know.

1080
01:07:33,578 --> 01:07:37,810
I mean, considering I've never been this
scared in my entire life. L... You know...

1081
01:07:37,882 --> 01:07:41,477
Listen. Once you get up there,
you're gonna be on your own.

1082
01:07:41,553 --> 01:07:45,614
- If anything should happen, I just wanted to...
- I know, Harry.

1083
01:07:45,690 --> 01:07:48,386
I'll, uh, try not to disappoint you.

1084
01:07:50,295 --> 01:07:52,229
Take care of yourself, kid.

1085
01:07:58,603 --> 01:08:02,266
[Man #1] Freedom's on the bridge.
Attention in the firing room.

1086
01:08:02,340 --> 01:08:07,403
- Oxidizer loading is complete.
- [Man #2] Independence on the bridge.

1087
01:08:07,479 --> 01:08:12,246
[Man #1] Attention all personnel. We are
T minus two hours to the program goal.

1088
01:08:20,391 --> 01:08:23,053
- Hey, Harry.
- [Harry] Yeah, Rock?

1089
01:08:23,128 --> 01:08:26,495
You know, we're sittin' on four million
pounds of fuel, one nuclear weapon...

1090
01:08:26,564 --> 01:08:29,590
and a thing that has
270,000 moving parts...

1091
01:08:29,667 --> 01:08:32,067
built by the lowest bidder.
[Grunts]

1092
01:08:32,137 --> 01:08:36,471
- Makes you feel good, doesn't it?
- Yeah.

1093
01:08:38,476 --> 01:08:40,967
- How ya doin', Oscar?
- Great.

1094
01:08:41,045 --> 01:08:43,479
I got that excited, scared feelin'...

1095
01:08:43,548 --> 01:08:46,711
like 98 percent excited,
2 percent scared.

1096
01:08:46,785 --> 01:08:50,778
Maybe more. It could be 2... It could
be 98 percent scared, 2 percent excited.

1097
01:08:50,855 --> 01:08:56,623
But that's what makes it so intense, is it's
so confused. I can't really figure it out.

1098
01:08:56,694 --> 01:08:59,561
Will you make mine really tight,
'cause I don't want to fall out?

1099
01:08:59,631 --> 01:09:01,565
