¤ With you
just like this ¤

2178
02:27:35,805 --> 02:27:40,071
¤ Well, I just wanna
hold you close ¤

2179
02:27:40,143 --> 02:27:44,714
¤ Feel your heart
so close to mine ¤

2180
02:27:44,847 --> 02:27:48,044
¤ And just stay here
in this moment ¤

2181
02:27:48,117 --> 02:27:52,781
¤ For all the rest of time ¤

2182
02:27:52,855 --> 02:27:55,085
¤ Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah ¤

2183
