¤ I don't wanna fall asleep ¤

2194
02:28:29,358 --> 02:28:33,294
¤ Yeah
I don't wanna miss a thing ¤

2195
02:31:30,239 --> 02:31:32,673
¤ [Woman Vocalizing]

2196
02:31:38,280 --> 02:31:43,183
¤ All my bags are packed
I'm ready to go ¤

2197
02:31:43,252 --> 02:31:47,120
¤ I'm standin' here
outside your door ¤

2198
02:31:47,189 --> 02:31:52,286
¤ I hate to wake you up
to say good-bye ¤

2199
02:31:54,063 --> 02:31:58,466
¤ But the dawn is breakin'
It's early morn ¤

2200
02:31:58,534 --> 02:32:02,231
¤ The taxi's waitin'
He's blowin' his horn ¤

2201
02:32:02,304 --> 02:32:05,671
¤ Already I'm ready
I'm so lonesome ¤

2202
02:32:05,741 --> 02:32:07,834
¤ I could die ¤

2203
02:32:09,645 --> 02:32:14,207
¤ So kiss me
and smile for me ¤

2204
02:32:14,283 --> 02:32:17,980
¤ Tell me
that you'll wait for me ¤

2205
02:32:18,053 --> 02:32:23,582
¤ Hold me like
you'll never let me go ¤

2206
02:32:24,827 --> 02:32:29,628
¤ 'Cause I'm leaving
on a jet plane ¤

2207
02:32:29,698 --> 02:32:34,101
¤ I don't know
when I'll be back again ¤

2208
02:32:34,169 --> 02:32:39,106
¤ Oh, babe
I hate to go ¤

2209
